<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>OTP Verification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f7;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding: 30px;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #4a90e2;
      text-align: center;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .otp {
      display: block;
      width: fit-content;
      margin: 20px auto;
      font-size: 28px;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      font-weight: bold;
      background-color: #f1f1f1;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #333;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
    }

    a {
      color: #4a90e2;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Verify Your Email</h1>
    <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
    <p>Thank you for registering! Use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to verify your account. This OTP is valid for <%= otpExpires %> minutes.</p>

    <span class="otp"><%= otp %></span>

    <p>If you did not request this OTP, please ignore this email.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= year %> MyApp. All rights reserved.
      <br>
      <a href="https://myapp.com">Visit our website</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
